    "The selected papers were identified using the search keywords (''HER'' OR ''Healthcare'' OR ''EMR'' OR ''Electronic Health Record'' OR ''Electronic Medical Record'') AND (''IoT'' OR ''Internet of Things'') AND ''Blockchain.''",
